cast.overview: A stunning cancer diagnosis spurs Abbie to seek a future girlfriend for fiancé and childhood sweetheart Sam, who's clueless when it comes to dating.
cast.title: Irreplaceable You

details.biography: Vanessa Carrasco is an actress residing in New York City, best known for her role in Law and Order SUV as Nydia; June Faria in New Amsterdam's 303, "Safe Enough", playing alongside Tyler Labine, as well as numerous short films, including Sleeping Beauty directed by Gabriela Quiroz. She also appeared in Irreplaceable You.
details.name: Vanessa Carrasco
